{"tid":2068782,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京肺炎大爆發！何栢良倡由北京來港人士需檢疫14日及留樣本","createTime":"2020-06-18T02:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T05:00:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3d3f274190ac1964a3b728148676a2305817c1fa","tid":2068782,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532730-20200618.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532730-20200618.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=c45a3f6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532730-20200618.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=445fc95e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532730-20200618.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n北京於一星期內新增百多宗新型肺炎確診個案，香港大學感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，中國以外的全球疫情仍未穩定，每日大約新增10萬宗個案，北京的風險雖然稍為調高，但認為其他國家對香港的風險是大一些。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良說，因應北京的情況，建議特區政府收緊做法，包括原本獲豁免檢疫而又是來自北京的人士，需要接受檢測及檢疫14日。另外，由北京經陸路返港的人士，亦需要如機場抵港人士一樣，要交深喉唾液樣本。 <br />\n<br />\n何栢良認為，政府因應本港經濟情況進一步放寬限聚令是可以理解，但當局整體檢測數量未有明顯改善，對於高危群組的監測亦一直採取被動做法，可能導致很遲才知道疫情的最新情況。"},{"pid":"88e27a83d72a19d2d197493fa07b3bfae16cefbd","tid":2068782,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:46:45.000Z","msg":"乜香港開左關？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9a81cc88e9bea14cbb5fabd0900ea43e37be76","tid":2068782,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:47:33.000Z","msg":"叫譚耀宗上去果班返黎要隔離啊"},{"pid":"f34fb00c03bbc2d0cfbbaa864b66fd37fc9658c5","tid":2068782,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:48:34.000Z","msg":"大膽港獨分子"},{"pid":"81105c4bfbe36d217e9dd437fb2283242a051a44","tid":2068782,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2